{
  "stem": "2718.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not too far, because if it's too far, we could've been cut off.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because they needed a certain number, and when the number was-- when the number was fulfilled, filled, then they stopped.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we kept a certain, certain distance with my father from each other, so they're not to be counted as any sort of relatives.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Nobody knew that-- nobody knew who was who.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nobody knew if it was somebody's brother or sister.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were only numbers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and so we were lucky-- we were lucky enough to, to manage to get through the health selections and then the transport selection.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we set out on our journey to Muhldorf.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I believe we were lucky, because a lot of people were sent from there to Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A lot of people were sent from there to Dachau and worse-- and worse places than Muhldorf.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How much worse, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Out of a thousand people when we arrived there on the first week of, of August there were 73 of us left on the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was-- con-- considering that the-- considering the, the misery, maybe it wasn't the worst.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Considering the, the, the food, considering the, the labor each one had to do, probably it was the worst.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But it couldn't have-- I don't know what the percentage was in other p-- in other camps.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It wasn't a vernichtungslager.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was an arbeitslager.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "That is what the good news was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was about the only good news about it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we talked about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He talked about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course he talked about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] We, we talked about [PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] every possibility.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
